er with <a href=\"http://localhost:8081/v2/check?language=en-US&#x26;text=my+text\">http://localhost:8081/v2/check?language=en-US&#x26;text=my+text</a></li>\n<li>In windows, run on <code>cmd</code> not <code>powershell</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://virtualwritingtutor.com/\">Grammar Check - Free Essay Checker | Virtual Writing Tutor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.onlinecorrection.com/\">Online Text Correction</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.grammarcheck.net/editor/\">Online Editor – Grammar Checker</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gingersoftware.com/grammarcheck\">Free Grammar Checker Online – Ginger Software</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.hemingwayapp.com/\">Hemingway Editor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.slickwrite.com/#!home\">Slick Write | Check your grammar. Proofread online.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.afterthedeadline.com/\">After the Deadline - Spell, Style, and Grammar Checker for WordPress, Firefox, TinyMCE, jQuery, and CKEditor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://writefull.com/\">Writefull</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/amperser/proselint\">amperser/proselint: A linter for prose.</a> writing assistant (dead project)</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://textlint.github.io/\">textlint · The pluggable linting tool for text and markdown</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/textlint-proofreader/hdongmdneapmhfblomidbafplpanpdmm\">textlint: Proofreader - Chrome Web Store</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/textlint/textlint/wiki/Collection-of-textlint-rule\">Collection of textlint rule · textlint/textlint Wiki</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/guardian/prosemirror-typerighter\">guardian/prosemirror-typerighter: The client-side companion to Typerighter. Match ranges with spellchecker-like semantics in Prosemirror documents.</a>  a plug in</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"grammar-checkers-add-ons\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grammar-